{
  "video_id": "buH_vs7LFzw",
  "title": "Steve Howard: Let's go all-in on selling sustainability",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12294.0,
      "end_time": 15470.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spent my life working on sustainability."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15470.0,
      "end_time": 17102.0,
      "text": "I set up a climate change NGO"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17102.0,
      "end_time": 18422.0,
      "text": "called The Climate Group."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18422.0,
      "end_time": 21813.0,
      "text": "I worked on forestry issues in WWF."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21813.0,
      "end_time": 23889.0,
      "text": "I worked on development and agriculture issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23889.0,
      "end_time": 25624.0,
      "text": "in the U.N. system."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25624.0,
      "end_time": 27548.0,
      "text": "About 25 years in total,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27548.0,
      "end_time": 30270.0,
      "text": "and then three years ago, I found myself talking to"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30271.0,
      "end_time": 33556.0,
      "text": "IKEA&#39;s CEO about joining his team."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33556.0,
      "end_time": 35581.0,
      "text": "Like many people here, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35582.0,
      "end_time": 39517.0,
      "text": "I want to maximize my personal impact in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39517.0,
      "end_time": 44203.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;m going to explain why I joined the team there."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44203.0,
      "end_time": 47100.0,
      "text": "But first, let&#39;s just take three numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47100.0,
      "end_time": 49800.0,
      "text": "The first number is three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49810.0,
      "end_time": 50641.0,
      "text": "three billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50641.0,
      "end_time": 52452.0,
      "text": "This is the number of people joining"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52452.0,
      "end_time": 54504.0,
      "text": "the global middle class by 2030,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54504.0,
      "end_time": 55812.0,
      "text": "coming out of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55813.0,
      "end_time": 58540.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s fantastic for them and their families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58540.0,
      "end_time": 61970.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;ve got two billion people in the global middle class today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61970.0,
      "end_time": 63394.0,
      "text": "and this swells that number to five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63394.0,
      "end_time": 66724.0,
      "text": "a big challenge when we already have resource scarcity."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66724.0,
      "end_time": 68601.0,
      "text": "The second number is six:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68601.0,
      "end_time": 70746.0,
      "text": "This is six degrees centigrade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70746.0,
      "end_time": 73310.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re heading towards in terms of global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73310.0,
      "end_time": 75361.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not heading towards one degree or three degrees"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75361.0,
      "end_time": 77709.0,
      "text": "or four degrees, we&#39;re heading toward six degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77709.0,
      "end_time": 80398.0,
      "text": "And if you think about it, all of the weird weather"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80398.0,
      "end_time": 82241.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been having the last few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82241.0,
      "end_time": 84823.0,
      "text": "much of that is due to just one degree warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84823.0,
      "end_time": 87118.0,
      "text": "and we need CO2 emissions to peak"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87118.0,
      "end_time": 89350.0,
      "text": "by the end of this decade globally"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89350.0,
      "end_time": 91770.0,
      "text": "and then come down."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91780.0,
      "end_time": 95149.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not inevitable, but we need to act decisively."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95149.0,
      "end_time": 96910.0,
      "text": "The third number is 12:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96910.0,
      "end_time": 98402.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the number of cities in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98403.0,
      "end_time": 100194.0,
      "text": "that had a million or more people"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100194.0,
      "end_time": 101627.0,
      "text": "when my grandmother was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101627.0,
      "end_time": 103247.0,
      "text": "You can see my grandmother there."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103247.0,
      "end_time": 105290.0,
      "text": "That was in the beginning of the last century."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 105290.0,
      "end_time": 107306.0,
      "text": "So just 12 cities. She was born in Manchester, England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 107306.0,
      "end_time": 109327.0,
      "text": "the ninth largest city in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 109327.0,
      "end_time": 112320.0,
      "text": "Now there are 500 cities, nearly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112320.0,
      "end_time": 114463.0,
      "text": "with a million people or more in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 114463.0,
      "end_time": 117806.0,
      "text": "And if you look at the century from 1950 to 2050,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 117807.0,
      "end_time": 121551.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the century when we build all the world&#39;s cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 121551.0,
      "end_time": 123961.0,
      "text": "the century that we&#39;re in the middle of right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 123961.0,
      "end_time": 126807.0,
      "text": "Every other century was kind of practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 126807.0,
      "end_time": 131625.0,
      "text": "and this lays down a blueprint for how we live."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131625.0,
      "end_time": 133380.0,
      "text": "So think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133380.0,
      "end_time": 136150.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re building cities like never before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136150.0,
      "end_time": 138676.0,
      "text": "bringing people out of poverty like never before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138676.0,
      "end_time": 141510.0,
      "text": "and changing the climate like never before."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 141510.0,
      "end_time": 144111.0,
      "text": "Sustainability has gone from a nice-to-do"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 144111.0,
      "end_time": 145775.0,
      "text": "to a must-do."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145776.0,
      "end_time": 148609.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about what we do right here, right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148609.0,
      "end_time": 152290.0,
      "text": "and for the rest of our working lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152290.0,
      "end_time": 154322.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to talk a little bit about"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154322.0,
      "end_time": 155695.0,
      "text": "what business can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 155695.0,
      "end_time": 157997.0,
      "text": "and what a business like IKEA can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157997.0,
      "end_time": 160664.0,
      "text": "and we have a sustainability strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160664.0,
      "end_time": 162661.0,
      "text": "called \"people and planet positive\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162661.0,
      "end_time": 166308.0,
      "text": "to help guide our business to have a positive impact on the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 166308.0,
      "end_time": 168442.0,
      "text": "Why would we not want to have a positive impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168443.0,
      "end_time": 171310.0,
      "text": "on the world as a business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171310.0,
      "end_time": 173519.0,
      "text": "Other companies have sustainability strategies."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173519.0,
      "end_time": 175357.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to refer to some of those as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175357.0,
      "end_time": 176894.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m just going to mention a few"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176894.0,
      "end_time": 179490.0,
      "text": "of the commitments as illustrations that we&#39;ve got."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 179490.0,
      "end_time": 181506.0,
      "text": "But first, let&#39;s think of customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181506.0,
      "end_time": 185331.0,
      "text": "We know from asking people from China to the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185331.0,
      "end_time": 188659.0,
      "text": "that the vast majority of people care about sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188659.0,
      "end_time": 190541.0,
      "text": "after the day-to-day issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190541.0,
      "end_time": 193118.0,
      "text": "the day-to-day issues of, how do I get my kids to school?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193118.0,
      "end_time": 195970.0,
      "text": "Can I pay the bills at the end of the month?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 195970.0,
      "end_time": 198559.0,
      "text": "Then they care about big issues like climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198559.0,
      "end_time": 202991.0,
      "text": "But they want it to be easy, affordable and attractive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 202991.0,
      "end_time": 204983.0,
      "text": "and they expect business to help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204983.0,
      "end_time": 207777.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re a little bit disappointed today."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207777.0,
      "end_time": 210410.0,
      "text": "So take your mind back and think"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210411.0,
      "end_time": 211998.0,
      "text": "of the first sustainable products."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211998.0,
      "end_time": 215911.0,
      "text": "We had detergents that could wash your whites grayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 215911.0,
      "end_time": 218965.0,
      "text": "We had the early energy-efficient light bulbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218965.0,
      "end_time": 220812.0,
      "text": "that took five minutes to warm up"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 220812.0,
      "end_time": 223883.0,
      "text": "and then you were left looking a kind of sickly color."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223883.0,
      "end_time": 227251.0,
      "text": "And we had the rough, recycled toilet paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227251.0,
      "end_time": 229983.0,
      "text": "So every time you pulled on a t-shirt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229983.0,
      "end_time": 232890.0,
      "text": "or switched the light on, or went to the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 232890.0,
      "end_time": 233758.0,
      "text": "or sometimes all three together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 233758.0,
      "end_time": 237203.0,
      "text": "you were reminded sustainability was about compromise."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 237203.0,
      "end_time": 240101.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t a great start."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 240101.0,
      "end_time": 242389.0,
      "text": "Today we have choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 242389.0,
      "end_time": 245686.0,
      "text": "We can make products that are beautiful or ugly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 245686.0,
      "end_time": 250487.0,
      "text": "sustainable or unsustainable, affordable or expensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 250487.0,
      "end_time": 252350.0,
      "text": "functional or useless."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252350.0,
      "end_time": 255215.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s make beautiful, functional, affordable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 255215.0,
      "end_time": 257535.0,
      "text": "sustainable products."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 257535.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259831.00000000003,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take the LED."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 259831.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263245.0,
      "text": "The LED is the next best thing to daylight."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 263245.0,
      "end_time": 266426.0,
      "text": "The old-fashioned lightbulbs, the incandescent bulbs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 266426.0,
      "end_time": 267933.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to ask for a show of hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 267934.0,
      "end_time": 270223.0,
      "text": "of how many of you still have them in your homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 270223.0,
      "end_time": 273450.0,
      "text": "wasting energy every time you switch them on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 273450.0,
      "end_time": 274482.0,
      "text": "change them after this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 274482.0,
      "end_time": 278175.0,
      "text": "or whether we have them on the stage here at TED or not --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 278175.0,
      "end_time": 281966.0,
      "text": "but those old incandescent light bulbs"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 281966.0,
      "end_time": 284988.0,
      "text": "really should have been sold as heaters."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 284988.0,
      "end_time": 286965.0,
      "text": "They were mis-sold for more than a hundred years."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 286965.0,
      "end_time": 289407.0,
      "text": "They produced heat and a little bit of light on the side."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 289407.0,
      "end_time": 291479.0,
      "text": "Now we have lights that produce light"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 291479.0,
      "end_time": 293171.0,
      "text": "and a little bit of heat on the side."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 293171.0,
      "end_time": 295997.0,
      "text": "You save 85 percent of the electricity with an LED"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 295997.0,
      "end_time": 298400.0,
      "text": "that you would have done in an old incandescent."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 298400.0,
      "end_time": 299775.0,
      "text": "And the best thing is, they&#39;ll also last"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 299775.0,
      "end_time": 301354.0,
      "text": "for more than 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 301354.0,
      "end_time": 302609.0,
      "text": "So think about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 302610.0,
      "end_time": 305106.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll change your smartphone seven or eight times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 305106.0,
      "end_time": 307182.0,
      "text": "probably more if you&#39;re in this audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 307182.0,
      "end_time": 309792.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll change your car, if you have one, three or four times."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 309792.0,
      "end_time": 312344.0,
      "text": "Your kids could go to school, go to college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 312344.0,
      "end_time": 314299.0,
      "text": "go away and have kids of their own, come back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 314299.0,
      "end_time": 315724.0,
      "text": "bring the grandkids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 315725.0,
      "end_time": 319611.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll have the same lightbulb saving you energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 319611.0,
      "end_time": 322450.0,
      "text": "So LEDs are fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 322450.0,
      "end_time": 323976.0,
      "text": "What we decided to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 323976.0,
      "end_time": 326929.0,
      "text": "was not to sell LEDs on the side marked up high"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 326929.0,
      "end_time": 329155.0,
      "text": "and continue to push all the old bulbs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 329155.0,
      "end_time": 331145.0,
      "text": "the halogens and the CFLs."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 331146.0,
      "end_time": 334760.0,
      "text": "We decided, over the next two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 334760.0,
      "end_time": 336591.0,
      "text": "we will ban the halogens and the CFLs ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 336591.0,
      "end_time": 337959.0,
      "text": "We will go all in."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 337959.0,
      "end_time": 339668.0,
      "text": "And this is what business needs to do: go all-in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 339668.0,
      "end_time": 341112.0,
      "text": "go 100 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 341112.0,
      "end_time": 342703.0,
      "text": "because then you stop investing in the old stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 342703.0,
      "end_time": 344857.0,
      "text": "you invest in the new stuff, you lower costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 344857.0,
      "end_time": 347186.0,
      "text": "you use your supply chain and your creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 347186.0,
      "end_time": 349943.0,
      "text": "and you get the prices down so everybody can afford"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 349943.0,
      "end_time": 352894.0,
      "text": "the best lights so they can save energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 352894.0,
      "end_time": 357440.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 357440.0,
      "end_time": 360173.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just about products in people&#39;s homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 360173.0,
      "end_time": 361817.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got to think about the raw materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 361817.0,
      "end_time": 363999.0,
      "text": "that produce our products."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 363999.0,
      "end_time": 365826.0,
      "text": "Obviously there&#39;s fantastic opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 365826.0,
      "end_time": 367320.0,
      "text": "with recycled materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 367320.0,
      "end_time": 370163.0,
      "text": "and we can and will go zero waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 370163.0,
      "end_time": 372151.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s opportunities in a circular economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 372151.0,
      "end_time": 375593.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re still dependent on natural, raw materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 375593.0,
      "end_time": 377383.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take cotton."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 377383.0,
      "end_time": 379111.0,
      "text": "Cotton&#39;s brilliant. Probably many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 379112.0,
      "end_time": 380523.0,
      "text": "are wearing cotton right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 380523.0,
      "end_time": 382570.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a brilliant textile in use."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 382570.0,
      "end_time": 383624.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really dirty in production."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 383624.0,
      "end_time": 387758.0,
      "text": "It uses lots of pesticides, lots of fertilizer, lots of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 387758.0,
      "end_time": 389378.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve worked with others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 389378.0,
      "end_time": 390979.0,
      "text": "with other businesses and NGOs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 390980.0,
      "end_time": 392836.0,
      "text": "on the Better Cotton Initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 392836.0,
      "end_time": 395500.0,
      "text": "working right back down to the farm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 395500.0,
      "end_time": 396840.0,
      "text": "and there you can halve the amount of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 396840.0,
      "end_time": 398671.0,
      "text": "and halve the chemical inputs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 398671.0,
      "end_time": 401567.0,
      "text": "the yields increase, and 60 percent of the costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 401567.0,
      "end_time": 403236.0,
      "text": "of running many of these farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 403236.0,
      "end_time": 405280.0,
      "text": "with farmers with low incomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 405280.0,
      "end_time": 406982.0,
      "text": "can be chemical imports."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 406983.0,
      "end_time": 409128.0,
      "text": "Yields increase, and you halve the input costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 409128.0,
      "end_time": 412300.0,
      "text": "Farmers are coming out of poverty. They love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 412300.0,
      "end_time": 413729.0,
      "text": "Already hundreds of thousands of farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 413730.0,
      "end_time": 415320.0,
      "text": "have been reached,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 415320.0,
      "end_time": 417984.0,
      "text": "and now we&#39;ve got 60 percent better cotton in our business."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 417984.0,
      "end_time": 419325.0,
      "text": "Again, we&#39;re going all-in."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 419326.0,
      "end_time": 422476.0,
      "text": "By 2015, we&#39;ll be 100 percent Better Cotton."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 422476.0,
      "end_time": 425462.0,
      "text": "Take the topic of 100 percent targets, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 425462.0,
      "end_time": 427134.0,
      "text": "People sometimes think that"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 427134.0,
      "end_time": 428599.0,
      "text": "100 percent&#39;s going to be hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 428599.0,
      "end_time": 430370.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve had the conversation in the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 430370.0,
      "end_time": 432212.0,
      "text": "Actually, we found 100 percent is easier to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 432212.0,
      "end_time": 434199.0,
      "text": "than 90 percent or 50 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 434199.0,
      "end_time": 435631.0,
      "text": "If you have a 90 percent target,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 435631.0,
      "end_time": 437510.0,
      "text": "everyone in the business finds a reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 437520.0,
      "end_time": 438857.0,
      "text": "to be in the 10 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 438857.0,
      "end_time": 442427.0,
      "text": "When it&#39;s 100 percent, it&#39;s kind of clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 442427.0,
      "end_time": 445317.0,
      "text": "and businesspeople like clarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 445317.0,
      "end_time": 447982.0,
      "text": "because then you just get the job done."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 447982.0,
      "end_time": 450730.0,
      "text": "So, wood. We know with forestry, it&#39;s a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 450730.0,
      "end_time": 452324.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got illegal logging"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 452324.0,
      "end_time": 455149.0,
      "text": "and deforestation still on a very large scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 455149.0,
      "end_time": 457849.0,
      "text": "or you can have fantastic, responsible forestry"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 457849.0,
      "end_time": 459984.0,
      "text": "that we can be proud of."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 459984.0,
      "end_time": 462660.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a simple choice, so we&#39;ve worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 462660.0,
      "end_time": 464609.0,
      "text": "for many years with the Forest Stewardship Council,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 464610.0,
      "end_time": 466980.0,
      "text": "with literally hundreds of other organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 466980.0,
      "end_time": 469420.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s a point here about collaboration."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 469420.0,
      "end_time": 471315.0,
      "text": "So hundreds of others, of NGOs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 471315.0,
      "end_time": 473897.0,
      "text": "of forest workers&#39; unions, and of businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 473897.0,
      "end_time": 475569.0,
      "text": "have helped create the Forest Stewardship Council,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 475569.0,
      "end_time": 477351.0,
      "text": "which sets standards for forestry"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 477351.0,
      "end_time": 479873.0,
      "text": "and then checks the forestry&#39;s good on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 479873.0,
      "end_time": 482116.0,
      "text": "Now together, through our supply chain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 482116.0,
      "end_time": 483983.0,
      "text": "with partners, we&#39;ve managed to certify"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 483983.0,
      "end_time": 486860.0,
      "text": "35 million hectares of forestry."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 486860.0,
      "end_time": 489397.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s about the size of Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 489397.0,
      "end_time": 491185.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve decided in the next three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 491185.0,
      "end_time": 493220.0,
      "text": "we will double the volume of certified material"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 493220.0,
      "end_time": 495358.0,
      "text": "we put through our business."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 495358.0,
      "end_time": 497998.0,
      "text": "So be decisive on these issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 497998.0,
      "end_time": 499969.0,
      "text": "Use your supply chain to drive good."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 499969.0,
      "end_time": 501995.0,
      "text": "But then it comes to your operations."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 501995.0,
      "end_time": 504645.0,
      "text": "Some things are certain, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 504645.0,
      "end_time": 507659.0,
      "text": "We know we&#39;ll use electricity in 20 or 30 years&#39; time."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 507660.0,
      "end_time": 510583.0,
      "text": "We know the sun will be shining somewhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 510583.0,
      "end_time": 513675.0,
      "text": "and the wind will still be blowing in 20 or 30 years&#39; time."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 513674.0,
      "end_time": 516327.0,
      "text": "So why not make our energy out of the sun and the wind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 516327.0,
      "end_time": 518554.0,
      "text": "And why not take control of it ourselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 518554.0,
      "end_time": 520914.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going 100 percent renewable."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 520914.0,
      "end_time": 523670.0,
      "text": "By 2020, we&#39;ll produce more renewable energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 523671.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525691.0,
      "text": "than the energy we consume as a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 525691.0,
      "end_time": 527667.0,
      "text": "For all of our stores, our own factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 527667.0,
      "end_time": 529450.0,
      "text": "our distribution centers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 529450.0,
      "end_time": 531498.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve installed 300,000 solar panels so far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 531499.0,
      "end_time": 534873.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve got 14 wind farms we own and operate"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 534873.0,
      "end_time": 537500.0,
      "text": "in six countries, and we&#39;re not done yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 537500.0,
      "end_time": 539284.0,
      "text": "But think of a solar panel."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 539284.0,
      "end_time": 541463.0,
      "text": "A solar panel pays for itself in seven or eight years."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 541463.0,
      "end_time": 542956.0,
      "text": "The electricity is free."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 542956.0,
      "end_time": 544761.0,
      "text": "Every time the sun comes out after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 544761.0,
      "end_time": 546195.0,
      "text": "the electricity is free."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 546196.0,
      "end_time": 548213.0,
      "text": "So this is a good thing for the CFO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 548213.0,
      "end_time": 550156.0,
      "text": "not just the sustainability guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 550156.0,
      "end_time": 553189.0,
      "text": "Every business can do things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 553190.0,
      "end_time": 556169.0,
      "text": "But then we&#39;ve got to look beyond our operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 556169.0,
      "end_time": 557918.0,
      "text": "and I think everybody would agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 557918.0,
      "end_time": 560290.0,
      "text": "that now business has to take full responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 560290.0,
      "end_time": 562493.0,
      "text": "for the impacts of your supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 562494.0,
      "end_time": 564810.0,
      "text": "Many businesses now, fortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 564810.0,
      "end_time": 566816.0,
      "text": "have codes of conduct and audit their supply chains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 566817.0,
      "end_time": 568863.0,
      "text": "but not every business. Far from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 568863.0,
      "end_time": 571377.0,
      "text": "And this came in IKEA actually in the &#39;90s."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 571377.0,
      "end_time": 573117.0,
      "text": "We found there was a risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 573118.0,
      "end_time": 575120.0,
      "text": "of child labor in the supply chain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 575120.0,
      "end_time": 577630.0,
      "text": "and people in the business were shocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 577630.0,
      "end_time": 580954.0,
      "text": "And it was clearly totally unacceptable, so then you have to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 580954.0,
      "end_time": 583980.0,
      "text": "So a code of conduct was developed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 583980.0,
      "end_time": 586490.0,
      "text": "and now we have 80 auditors out in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 586490.0,
      "end_time": 588790.0,
      "text": "every day making sure all our factories"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 588800.0,
      "end_time": 590364.0,
      "text": "secure good working conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 590364.0,
      "end_time": 591913.0,
      "text": "and protect human rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 591913.0,
      "end_time": 594174.0,
      "text": "and make sure there is no child labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 594174.0,
      "end_time": 596334.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just as simple as making sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 596334.0,
      "end_time": 598366.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no child labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 598366.0,
      "end_time": 600566.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got to say that&#39;s not enough today."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 600566.0,
      "end_time": 602614.0,
      "text": "I think we&#39;d all agree that children"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 602614.0,
      "end_time": 604810.0,
      "text": "are the most important people in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 604810.0,
      "end_time": 606707.0,
      "text": "and the most vulnerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 606707.0,
      "end_time": 608955.0,
      "text": "So what can a business do today"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 608955.0,
      "end_time": 610839.0,
      "text": "to actually use your total value chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 610839.0,
      "end_time": 613118.0,
      "text": "to support a better quality of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 613118.0,
      "end_time": 614706.0,
      "text": "and protect child rights?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 614706.0,
      "end_time": 617300.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve worked with UNICEF and Save the Children"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 617300.0,
      "end_time": 619478.0,
      "text": "on developing some new business principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 619478.0,
      "end_time": 620943.0,
      "text": "with children&#39;s rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 620943.0,
      "end_time": 622760.0,
      "text": "Increasing numbers of businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 622760.0,
      "end_time": 624280.0,
      "text": "are signing up to these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 624280.0,
      "end_time": 626742.0,
      "text": "but actually in a survey, many business leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 626743.0,
      "end_time": 629610.0,
      "text": "said they thought their business had nothing to do with children."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 629610.0,
      "end_time": 633109.0,
      "text": "So what we decided to do was, we will look"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 633109.0,
      "end_time": 634670.0,
      "text": "and ask ourselves the tough questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 634670.0,
      "end_time": 636733.0,
      "text": "with partners who know more than us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 636734.0,
      "end_time": 639691.0,
      "text": "what can we do to go beyond our business"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 639691.0,
      "end_time": 641533.0,
      "text": "to help improve the lives of children?"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 641533.0,
      "end_time": 643352.0,
      "text": "We also have a foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 643352.0,
      "end_time": 645247.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s committed to work through partners"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 645247.0,
      "end_time": 647870.0,
      "text": "and help improve the lives and protect the rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 647870.0,
      "end_time": 650737.0,
      "text": "of 100 million children by 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 650737.0,
      "end_time": 652413.0,
      "text": "You know the phrase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 652413.0,
      "end_time": 655791.0,
      "text": "you can manage what you measure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 655791.0,
      "end_time": 660441.0,
      "text": "Well, you should measure what you care about."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 660441.0,
      "end_time": 661990.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re not measuring things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 661990.0,
      "end_time": 664734.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t care and you don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 664734.0,
      "end_time": 666903.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s take an example, measure the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 666903.0,
      "end_time": 669600.0,
      "text": "that are important in your business."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 669600.0,
      "end_time": 671343.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it about time that businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 671343.0,
      "end_time": 674320.0,
      "text": "were led equally by men and women?"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 674321.0,
      "end_time": 677304.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 677304.0,
      "end_time": 682446.0,
      "text": "So we know for our 17,000 managers across IKEA"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 682446.0,
      "end_time": 685410.0,
      "text": "that 47 percent are women today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 685410.0,
      "end_time": 687805.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not enough, and we want to close the gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 687806.0,
      "end_time": 690930.0,
      "text": "and follow it all the way through to senior management."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 690930.0,
      "end_time": 692939.0,
      "text": "And we do not want to wait another hundred years."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 692939.0,
      "end_time": 695897.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve launched a women&#39;s open network"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 695898.0,
      "end_time": 697423.0,
      "text": "this week in IKEA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 697423.0,
      "end_time": 699599.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll do whatever it takes to lead the change."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 699599.0,
      "end_time": 701140.0,
      "text": "So the message here is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 701140.0,
      "end_time": 703398.0,
      "text": "measure what you care about and lead the change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 703398.0,
      "end_time": 706401.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t wait a hundred years."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 706401.0,
      "end_time": 708838.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve gone from sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 708838.0,
      "end_time": 714740.0,
      "text": "being a nice-to-do to a must-do. It&#39;s a must-do."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 714740.0,
      "end_time": 717226.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s still nice to do, but it&#39;s a must-do."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 717226.0,
      "end_time": 722161.0,
      "text": "And everybody can do something on this as an individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 722161.0,
      "end_time": 724357.0,
      "text": "Be a discerning consumer."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 724357.0,
      "end_time": 726550.0,
      "text": "Vote with your wallets."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 726550.0,
      "end_time": 728234.0,
      "text": "Search out the companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 728235.0,
      "end_time": 730930.0,
      "text": "that are acting on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 730930.0,
      "end_time": 733977.0,
      "text": "But also, there are other businesses already acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 733977.0,
      "end_time": 736122.0,
      "text": "I mentioned renewable energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 736122.0,
      "end_time": 738439.0,
      "text": "You go to Google or Lego,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 738440.0,
      "end_time": 740700.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re going 100 percent renewable too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 740700.0,
      "end_time": 742670.0,
      "text": "in the same way that we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 742670.0,
      "end_time": 745193.0,
      "text": "On having really good sustainability strategies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 745193.0,
      "end_time": 748437.0,
      "text": "there are companies like Nike, Patagonia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 748437.0,
      "end_time": 750591.0,
      "text": "Timberland, Marks & Spencer."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 750591.0,
      "end_time": 752749.0,
      "text": "But I don&#39;t think any of those businesses would say"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 752749.0,
      "end_time": 755140.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re perfect. We certainly wouldn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 755140.0,
      "end_time": 757380.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll make mistakes going forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 757380.0,
      "end_time": 759897.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s about setting a clear direction, being transparent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 759897.0,
      "end_time": 761586.0,
      "text": "having a dialogue with the right partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 761586.0,
      "end_time": 766102.0,
      "text": "and choosing to lead on the issues that really count."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 766102.0,
      "end_time": 768901.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re a business leader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 768901.0,
      "end_time": 771856.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re not already weaving sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 771856.0,
      "end_time": 774264.0,
      "text": "right into the heart of your business model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 774264.0,
      "end_time": 776155.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d urge you to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 776155.0,
      "end_time": 778130.0,
      "text": "And together, we can help create"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 778130.0,
      "end_time": 780130.0,
      "text": "a sustainable world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 780130.0,
      "end_time": 782259.0,
      "text": "and, if we get it right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 782259.0,
      "end_time": 783748.0,
      "text": "we can make sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 783748.0,
      "end_time": 785370.0,
      "text": "affordable for the many people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 785370.0,
      "end_time": 787670.0,
      "text": "not a luxury for the few."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 787670.0,
      "end_time": 788424.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 788424.0,
      "end_time": 793235.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}